Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.21,0:01:27.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen,\Nwe are now preparing for landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.05,0:01:30.62,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Please fasten your seatbelts tightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.62,0:01:33.32,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Did I wake you up? Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:38.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Say, that's from the missile attack\Nwe saw on the news in D.C., right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:43.35,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:48.80,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And there's a bunch of other places like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.80,0:01:52.04,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Are they from missiles too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:54.21,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:56.04,Font 1,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.04,0:02:01.98,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But those craters are from\NCareless Monday, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:05.01,Font 1,,0,0,0,,"Careless Monday"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.43,0:02:13.33,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, today is Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.33,0:02:17.77,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(371,120)}Episode 2:\NMelancholy Monday
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:24.67,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\fnTahoma}Inbox
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:24.67,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs36\pos(414,325)}Osugi\NOsugi\NOsugi\NOsugi\NOsugi\NOsugi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:23.34,Font 1,,0,0,0,,They're all from osugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:31.34,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I didn't make it in time for\Nthat job interview after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.51,0:02:33.41,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\fnTahoma}One Boy and Girl Were Saved
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:40.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,They're saying a plane crashed\Nbecause of the missile.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:42.59,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(200,140)}The Eleventh Missile!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:42.59,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(305,355)}One Boy and Girl Were Saved
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.69,0:02:45.46,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It looks like a six-year-old boy\Nand girl miraculously survived...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.59,0:02:49.20,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(200,140)}The Eleventh Missile!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.59,0:02:49.20,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(289,344)}Survivors of the Plane Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:48.06,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No way, the missile killed people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:49.46,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:52.63,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But there were no casualties at all last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:55.90,Font 1,,0,0,0,,oh, so that's why everything is so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:03:00.04,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, there\Nwere no casualties before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,0:03:03.14,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, nobody died on Careless Monday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:06.08,Font 1,,0,0,0,,--Why not?!\N--"Why not"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:08.65,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(335,270)}Caller:\NOsugi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:11.82,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:15.62,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, Saki? Thank goodness!\NAre you at the airport already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:17.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Sounds like she arrived on schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:19.23,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:23.73,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We're all fine. There wasn't any\Ndamage at your sister's place, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:25.00,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.74,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You've got an interview with that\Ncompany that's hiring you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:31.34,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We're in a car on our way to\Npick you up. Yeah. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:35.78,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Osugi, you're saying that easily,\Nbut we'll never make it on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:37.01,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:41.32,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine, so just wait there.\NWe'll be sure to make it on time--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:43.31,Font 1,,0,0,0,,S-Saki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:47.82,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We got cut off. I wonder if\Nit's because of that missile?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:49.52,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:54.76,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What's with all of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:57.30,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You guys sure are close.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:04:00.77,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You just got back from that trip\Nto America together two days ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:04.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,More importantly, there's no\Nplace for Saki to sit now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:10.65,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:12.45,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:14.64,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Now you've got a call, Takizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,--Hello?\N--This is Juiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:20.29,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:23.99,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Number 9, you've entered the\NSelecao system's effective range.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:26.79,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Please immediately carry out your\Nobligation as one of the "haves."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:28.90,Font 1,,0,0,0,,My obligation as one of the "haves"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:30.63,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hang on a second, Juiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:32.13,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Juiz?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:35.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello! My name is Morimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:40.24,Font 1,,0,0,0,,--Could you put me through to\NYamada in Human Resources?\N--I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:44.38,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If you know why I erased\Nmy memories, please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:48.82,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I don't know; I merely procured\Nthe means for you to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:53.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If you have any further requests,\Nplease don't hesitate to let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:05:00.53,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The remaining money available\Nto you totals 8,262,307,719 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:02.43,Font 1,,0,0,0,,8.2 billion yen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:05.93,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You have a duty to use all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:08.40,Font 1,,0,0,0,,"Duty"? Not a right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:11.37,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Correct. I am your concierge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:14.74,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I will continue to help you\Nto the best of my ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:16.44,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I don't really get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:19.71,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but does that basically mean\Nyou'll do anything I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:22.18,Font 1,,0,0,0,,In plain terms, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:26.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,okay, then-- I'm in the airport\Nright now, and I'd like to leave fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:29.25,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Well? Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:37.23,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Accepted. Noblesse oblige. I pray\Nyou shall continue to be a savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:43.40,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Number 9? Is that me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:47.40,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, please clear a path.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:55.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:06:00.62,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Please go question a\N24-year-old unemployed man
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:04.25,Font 1,,0,0,0,,suspected of being involved in the\Nmass disappearance of the NEETs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:10.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If a bunch of shut-ins actually\Nleft home, isn't that a good thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:13.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:31.29,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(304,208)}Selecao Activity History
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:23.31,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs20\pos(338,399)}[Fee for having an immigration official pick \Nhim up in a golf cart]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:20.51,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Number 9?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:23.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What's this? It's an obvious bribe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:31.29,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(318,394)}[Plum chewing gum at a Haneda Airport store]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:27.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And plum chewing gum?\NHe's totally thoughtless...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:31.31,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:36.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:40.36,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Wow, so you can also use it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:41.62,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(363,264)}Selecao Activity History
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:41.62,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(301,373)}[Plum chewing gum at a Haneda Airport store]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.30,0:06:44.26,Font 1,,0,0,0,,He's gotta be a star!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:54.94,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:57.98,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Um, this is super-embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:07:00.65,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they've got you\Nmixed up with someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:03.52,Font 1,,0,0,0,,or wait, are you actually a celebrity?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:05.28,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:12.73,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:15.56,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Do you have any plans right now or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:16.73,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:22.47,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The truth is, my plans for today\Nare all thrown off, so I'm free now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:27.31,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Would you like to go grab a cup\Nof tea with me or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:30.24,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Um, sorry for saying something so weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:34.15,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but actually I have no clue who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:39.35,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I have no memory of anything\Nbefore the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:44.42,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I can't remember my name,\Nor what I've been doing, or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:50.36,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So, the first thing I have\Nto do is figure out who I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:54.04,Font 1,,0,0,0,,so I think I'll start by going\Nto the address on my passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:58.03,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So let's say goodbye here. See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:03.51,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:09.28,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Number 9 is supposed to have been dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:12.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Maybe somebody picked up his phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:16.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,otherwise nobody but me\Nwould use it for stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:23.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What was with him? I thought\Nwe were getting along so well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:34.13,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What an awful face.\NMaybe I didn't smile enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:40.54,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Your smile was just great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:44.15,Font 1,,0,0,0,,--Hi.\N--What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:45.79,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You're breaking social rules here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:49.15,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Um, where is Toyosu, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:56.06,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And now he's just waltzed onto the monorail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:08:59.16,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I did want to get a look at him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:14.35,Font 1,,0,0,0,,--What is it?\N--This address is right next to a crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:17.42,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Where a missile hit on Careless Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:20.66,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I think this area is in ruins now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder if my house is gone, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:29.60,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, just how many of those craters are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:32.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Why was there even a missile\Nattack in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:38.34,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I think there were eleven missiles total,\Nif you count yesterday's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:43.64,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but last year\Non Monday, November 22nd,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:45.98,Font 1,,0,0,0,,they suddenly came flying at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:48.98,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The SDF and the police and the politicians
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:53.72,Font 1,,0,0,0,,never dreamed Japan would be\Nsubject to a missile attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:57.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So on a special newscast, the Prime\NMinister actually said, "I was careless."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:10:00.46,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And that's why it's called "Careless Monday"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:06.20,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yep. And afterwards, it came to\Nlight that there were no deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:11.31,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The internet and the mass media went\Ncrazy trying to find out who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:13.24,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Saying it was a neighboring country's attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:18.71,Font 1,,0,0,0,,or an American conspiracy,\Nor that our government did it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.71,0:10:22.32,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But the whole thing was just too improbable,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:26.15,Font 1,,0,0,0,,so people kind of lost their sense of crisis...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:28.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It was rash of us, but we got a little excited,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:33.19,Font 1,,0,0,0,,anticipating that maybe something\Neven bigger would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:52.61,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Number 9?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:01.09,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(267,28)}Selecao Activity History
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:01.09,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(289,148)\fn\fs18}[Exit monorail at Tennoz isle]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:01.09,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(314,251)\fn\fs18}[Boarded monorail at Haneda]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:01.09,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(328,325)\fn\fs18}[Plum chewing gum at a Haneda Airport store]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:04.02,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I was right. Dammit, he should still be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:08.86,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I lost him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:12.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:15.27,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We have the same cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:21.38,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Have you lost your memory too, Mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:25.11,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:29.48,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing! Sorry, I was just curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:30.62,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:34.59,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hold on there, kid. Are you Selecao?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:36.06,Font 1,,0,0,0,,"Selecao"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:45.60,Font 1,,0,0,0,,These are dangerous times.\NI'm going to check your ID just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.43,Font 1,,0,0,0,,My ID?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:53.74,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Akira Takizawa, with an address in Toyosu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:57.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I see. Next time you say crazy\Nstuff to me, I'll haul you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:11:59.15,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:01.61,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Okay, Detective, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:08.12,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So he's Selecao No. 9?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.99,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That was bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:24.44,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You can go when the boat gets here.\NI think I can make it the rest of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:28.18,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Here's your coffee, and 760 yen in change.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:32.71,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Thanks. You can keep the change.\NYou haven't got any cash, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:35.61,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Great, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:42.86,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I hope your place is still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:46.62,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Well, if it's not, I'll figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:54.40,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I know-- since I'm such a blank slate,\Ntell me about you instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:55.54,Font 1,,0,0,0,,About me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:59.53,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, as much as you can\Nbefore the boat gets here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:07.72,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm a senior in college,\Nand I'll be working starting in April...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.82,Font 1,,0,0,0,,oh, so you'll be working. Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:12.59,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Where my sister's husband used to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:14.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So you have an older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.05,0:13:18.76,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Um, I don't want you to walk\Non eggshells with me about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:22.43,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but I don't have any parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:26.70,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It was an accident.\NMy sister was already married,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:29.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and I thought I'd forget about\Ncollege and start working,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:32.61,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but she and her husband took\Nover the family business for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:34.94,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and let me go to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.94,0:13:36.58,Font 1,,0,0,0,,She's a nice sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:38.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Ryosuke, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:41.42,Font 1,,0,0,0,,oh, he's Sis's husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:47.09,Font 1,,0,0,0,,She had a baby last year, which\Nmakes four of us living together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:49.25,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What's Ryosuke like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:54.59,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Stop rushing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:14:01.47,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Ryosuke is a very sincere person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:04.37,Font 1,,0,0,0,,They've been going out\Nsince my sister was in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:09.24,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I knew they'd get married\Nfrom the moment I met him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:10.58,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So he's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:14.08,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess my sister's got decent taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:17.99,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Sounds good. It really feels like you're family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.99,0:14:20.62,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But it's not all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:24.12,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed that I've been\Nsuch a burden on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:25.72,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:38.14,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Listening to you, I think I got\Njust one of my memories back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:40.24,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:44.78,Font 1,,0,0,0,,When I was about five, someone in\Na department store gave me 500 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:48.12,Font 1,,0,0,0,,They said, "Go buy whatever\Nyou want with this."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:50.99,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And when I hesitated about doing it alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:57.52,Font 1,,0,0,0,,they said, "It's okay. If you've got money,\Na kid's as good as an adult."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:15:01.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I forget what I bought, but I clearly remember
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:06.97,Font 1,,0,0,0,,that the man at the register\Nbowed deeply to me when I paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:13.27,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I got all happy, and turned around\Nto say that Mom had been right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:15.54,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is a memory of my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:22.12,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But when I turned around, she was gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:25.45,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and I think I never saw her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:28.81,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:38.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But hey, I remembered that I had a mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:49.33,Font 1,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:09.93,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Wait... I don't even have\Nyour email address yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:33.75,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hit me, Bartender.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:41.86,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The monorail, bubble gum,\Na bribe for Immigration...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:46.10,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(277,39)}Selecao Activity History
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:46.10,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(321,297)}[Fee for having an immigration\Nofficial pick him up in a golf cart]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:46.10,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(320,417)}[Download brainwashing\Nprogram from Ato Harima\NNeuroscience Institute]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:45.27,Font 1,,0,0,0,,A brainwashing program from the\NHarima Neuroscience Institute...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:51.77,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but he did\Nsomething to his own memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:55.38,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(265,36)}Selecao Activity History
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:55.38,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(295,317)}[Two weeks worth of\Nconvenience store food for\N20,000 delivered]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:55.38,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(333,415)}[Urban Management Shopping\NMall purchase fee]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:54.48,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And then there's the shopping mall in Toyosu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:59.08,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But how is this supposed to be helping Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:02.25,Font 1,,0,0,0,,In a sense, this guy might\Nbe even worse than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.89,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You're in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:08.09,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, looks like good luck's\Nstarting to come my way again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:10.46,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear it, Mr. Kondou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:14.16,Font 1,,0,0,0,,In that case, please hurry up\Nand return my 20 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:20.26,Font 1,,0,0,0,,or you can give me a list of the\NPD's multiple debtors instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.30,0:17:26.34,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yeah. I was held up\Nforever at the airport...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:32.15,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll explain that tomorrow.\NI'm staying at Micchon's tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:34.17,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:39.82,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, you said you went to New York, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:43.16,Font 1,,0,0,0,,--Yeah.\N--So did you go to Fifth Avenue?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:47.63,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I went to Tiffany's!\NI didn't buy anything, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.63,0:17:51.63,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This is Times Square. I went\Nto see "The Lion King" at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:54.60,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Wow. Where else did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:58.11,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I went to Central Park,\NI saw the Statue of Liberty,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:17:59.94,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I walked the Brooklyn Bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:01.48,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That Gothic bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:03.68,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yep! You know your stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:05.80,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I've just seen it in movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:11.55,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This bridge had a time portal\Nin that Meg Ryan movie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:15.66,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I don't really watch movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:19.89,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Huh. I thought any girl would've seen that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:24.00,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Damn, my memory for\Nmovies is awfully vivid, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:28.74,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What others do you remember?\NMaybe we'll find a clue to your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.74,0:18:31.31,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What's your favorite movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:36.74,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Well, I've forgotten just\Nabout everything about myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:39.51,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:42.22,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:44.22,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That's the Freedom Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:45.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Freedom Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:48.76,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The new building on the site of Ground Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:51.06,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You mean as in 9/11?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:55.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Huh... I don't think this has\Nmade it into the movies yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:19:00.43,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It was mysterious; so smooth and pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:03.44,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see Ground Zero,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:07.24,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but there's no trace anymore\Nof how it was ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:13.08,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But somehow I feel like I mustn't\Nforget about that attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:18.55,Font 1,,0,0,0,,C'mere a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:27.02,Font 1,,0,0,0,,How's that? Ground Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:31.47,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Can I have a copy of this photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.47,0:19:33.06,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:37.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I don't know how. You do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.99,0:19:57.06,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kondou, if things keep up this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.06,0:20:01.16,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I'll be forced\Nto visit your place of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:02.76,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:05.90,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Juiz, kill these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:10.60,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Accepted. Noblesse oblige. I pray\Nyou shall continue to be a savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:12.40,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Shutup
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.75,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:21.28,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do my life over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:24.65,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Has being cornered like\Nthis made you go crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.65,0:20:26.24,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:35.82,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:44.71,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Him too, Juiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:46.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:48.47,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:55.17,Font 1,,0,0,0,,These days, a lone cop can't carry out\Njustice no matter how hard he tries.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:00.78,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(361,159)}Selecao Activity History
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:00.78,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(319,268)}[Kill the three men\Nin front of him]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:00.78,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(293,329)}[Social expenses]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:04.29,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever. Just you wait, Number 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.29,0:21:07.89,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'll take over your obligations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:15.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The night is a seal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:22.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If we mix in some bewilderment, it will end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:34.85,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If we're in danger of wavering,\Nlet's just abandon our reasons
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.09,0:21:42.55,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We drown in dreams again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:46.70,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The future stretches on uncertainly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:58.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I can still forgive you,\NI can still know the meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:22:02.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The night exists to be listened to closely
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:09.06,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I can copy that reason, and change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:19.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind cutting off\Nthe future to know your breath
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.87,0:22:25.07,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind cutting off the future